OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGreater Manchester PC      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsacked for causing man's   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flife-changing injuries     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Greater Manchester Police (GMP)      
OL,6, officer whose "reckless" driving       
OL,7, "resulted in a man's life-changing     
OL,8, injuries" has been sacked.             
OL,10,FThe man was dragged along by a police  
OL,11,Fvan, driven by PC Daniel Gaffney,      
OL,12,Foutside a hospital in April 2018 and he
OL,13,Ffell face first into the road.         
OL,15,FThe Independent Office for Police      
OL,16,FConduct (IOPC) said PC Gaffney's       
OL,17,Fbehaviour amounted to gross misconduct.
OL,19,FHis account of the incident amounted to
OL,20,Foperational dishonesty, it added.      
